summary: Twitter is stressing me out because everyone keeps (I can't think of another word so we are gonna use "harrassing") but everyone...
body: Twitter is stressing me out because everyone keeps (I can’t think of another word so we are gonna use “harrassing”) but everyone keeps basically harrassing Dan for not posting when it is absolutely fine that he is not posting. Let him have his break, let him breathe and enjoy life outside of youtube. Phil did the same thing and came back eventually, so Dan will too. Dan can see everything we post, no doubt in my mind we might be pissing him off. Let him breathe I can’t stress it enough. Okay, I’m going back to sleep now.
